36#ifndef __store_int_h__
37#define __store_int_h__
38
39struct krb5_storage_data {
40 void *data;
41 ssize_t (*fetch)(struct krb5_storage_data*, void*, size_t);
42 ssize_t (*store)(struct krb5_storage_data*, const void*, size_t);
43 off_t (*seek)(struct krb5_storage_data*, off_t, int);
44 int (*trunc)(struct krb5_storage_data*, off_t);
45 int (*fsync)(struct krb5_storage_data*);
46 void (*free)(struct krb5_storage_data*);
47 krb5_flags flags;
48 int eof_code;
49 size_t max_alloc;
50};
51
52#endif /* __store_int_h__ */
